divs: Sighting Detailsi was driving down the interstate with my wife and i all of a sudden saw the swarm straight ahead in the sky im guessing about 2-500 feet in the air and i pulled off the shoulder and tried to record with my cell but it did not pick up on my phone my wife did get a couple of photos before the last two disappeared they appeared to be moving straight across the sky and when they got to a certain spot they would appear to flicker out one at a time as they reached that particular point i took my wifes phone and zoomed in on the photos and the objects appear to be boomerang shaped but could be because of the movement not sure.
Summary: was about 30 or 40 objects in a swarm like formation
